==English==
=== Etymology ===
From Middle French '''''piquant''''' "pricking, stimulating, irritating"

=== Adjective ===
[[Category:English adjectives]]
'''piquant'''
# [[engaging]]; [[charming]]
# favorably [[stimulating]] to the [[palate]]; pleasantly [[spicy]]; stimulating 
# (archaic) causing hurt feelings; [[scathing]]

==== Translations ====
* {{io}} : [[pikar|pika]]

=== Adverb ===
[[Category:English adverbs]]
'''piquantly'''
# with strong spice; [[spicily]]

=== Noun ===
[[Category:English nouns]]
'''piquantness''' ''or'' '''piquancy'''
# the degree to which something is '''piquant'''

